{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 400°F. Line a baking pan with parchment and set aside.","Place oil, onion, garlic and chili into mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 7<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula, then sauté <b>3 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>.","Add cayenne pepper, paprika, tomatoes and salt. Place Varoma into position, weigh in potatoes, secure Varoma lid and steam <b>20 min\/212°F\/speed 1<b>. Set Varoma aside and <strong>insert measuring cup,<\/strong> then blend <b>30 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer sauce into a large bowl and cover to keep warm.","Place steamed potatoes onto prepared baking pan and top with sliced chorizo. Bake for 20 minutes (400°F). Remove from oven and stir potatoes and chorizo to ensure even cooking. Return pan to the oven and bake a further 25-30 minutes (400°F) or until potatoes are golden and chorizo is sizzling.","Transfer potatoes and chorizo into a serving bowl and serve warm sauce on the side."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["1 tbsp olive oil","2 oz red onion, quartered","2 garlic cloves","1 - 2 fresh bird's eye chili, seeds removed (optional), to taste","1 pinch cayenne pepper","1 pinch smoked paprika","1 can diced tomatoes (approx. 28 oz)","¼ - ½ tsp sea salt, to taste","28 - 30 oz Yukon gold potatoes, peeled and cut into pieces (approx. 1 in.)","16 oz chorizo sausages, thinly sliced (¼ in.)"]}],"id":"r109199","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-4-pkzzT-Noc\/XZMuHvm_ACI\/AAAAAAAAaBc\/ghbCj0UOjCQ9K96Nj4vXNvCNg5pevg3ygCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_AI3DhQnA3JfWyP1r.png","title":"Potatoes with Chorizo","publishedAt":"2017-08-11T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"11 g","fat":"10.5 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"13 g","calories":"828 kJ \/ 197 kcal"},"usefulItems":"parchment paper, large bowl, baking pan (approx. 18 in. x 12 in. x 2 in.), serving bowl, oven","hintsAndTricks":["This is a classic tapas dish served throughout Spain.","Removing skin from chorizo sausages befor